{"tid":892984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警鑑證科人員用虛假報價單認罪候判","createTime":"2018-11-07T09:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T04:53:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ced20e8946eaf717fd54aa51122dfc63a87c5ada","tid":892984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1427097_1_L_20181107171245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1427097_1_L_20181107171245.jpg&h=37894ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警務處鑑證科高級攝影員張劍峯涉嫌使用虛假報價單，購買34萬元貨品，今日在東區裁判法院承認八項使用虛假文書罪，案件押後至本月28日判刑，以便索取背景及社會服務令報告。<br />\n<br />\n54歲被告張劍峯，職責包括為攝影課採購貨品及服務。案情指被告涉嫌於2014年9月10日至2017年8月1日期間，使用9份以3間公司名義發出的虛假報價單，為警務處鑑證科購入總值逾34萬元的貨品及服務，誘使兩名鑑證科上司接受該9份文書。"},{"pid":"5102cb5dbb728eb7a42655a1df89586fc3ee50dd","tid":892984,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"阿sir買野使你教"},{"pid":"bfea26a4bf982b3690a6f31691ed1f76e2550c68","tid":892984,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e00274be15016a90f43b2fb3cc02de84616ffa","tid":892984,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}